author: Patrick Cc:
description:
This video covers the rise and fall of Hulk Hogan, one of the most iconic figures in professional wrestling. It breaks down how he maintained his larger-than-life persona for decades, and how personal scandals—including infidelity, racism, and legal battles—ultimately damaged his reputation and legacy.
